.*******************************************************************************
.*                            CONSTANTS DECLARATION                            *
.*******************************************************************************
DRAW      INIT      "*-------------------------------------------------------":
                    "----------------------------*"                    *I-57547
FINISH    INIT      "Finish"
START     INIT      "Start"
.
Z5        INIT      "zzzzz"
Z30       INIT      "zzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzz"
.
PRGID     INIT      "IBAPMS71"
